nodes.text: Hunnos Jarkey's Ranch was a ranch located near the city of Theed, on the planet Naboo during the Galactic Civil War. Circa 1 ABY, the wanted murderer Hunnos Jarkey lived secretly in the ranch after he escaped the Royal Naboo Security Forces. For his protection, he recruited a small army of Naboo pirates and fortified the area. Nevertheless, Hunnos Jarkey and all pirates were killed during a RSF assault.
